    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">预计试玩时长：2–4小时</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/26722756e26317b4b4b9b3f79b0c3cbc.avif?t=1770871236\" width=1560 height=3604 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>卡牌肉鸽游戏 (Roguelike)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《永恒之藤》(Everwane) 结合了卡牌肉鸽、英雄组队选择和银河恶魔城 (Metroidvania) 元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">管理你的酒馆，探索世界，创造出英雄能力、卡牌、遗物和神器最不可思议的组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/f9eea107938e2e5fb9a9de8152c45b4b.poster.avif?t=1770871236\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/f9eea107938e2e5fb9a9de8152c45b4b.webm?t=1770871236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/f9eea107938e2e5fb9a9de8152c45b4b.mp4?t=1770871236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 单英雄或多英雄游玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 战术定位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 角色协同作用，实现高级战术</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 复杂的首领 (Boss) 战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 酒馆管理</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 细致入微、手工绘制的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 引人入胜的剧情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 危险的地下城</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 互动沉浸式环境</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">• 独特的遭遇系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/00bb5eff986ccc8d218600b1e41dfbe8.poster.avif?t=1770871236\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/00bb5eff986ccc8d218600b1e41dfbe8.webm?t=1770871236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/00bb5eff986ccc8d218600b1e41dfbe8.mp4?t=1770871236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>关于游戏体验与世界 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">这个世界是精美的手绘，充满了互动元素和秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在游历其间的土地时，你将解锁神秘地点、地下城和故事情节任务，加深对这个丰富游戏世界的理解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">我们付出了巨大的努力来激活和充实这个世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏机制、世界观和情节的结合，构成了独特的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">冒险等待着你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/7a7c1b02226e48a114c43612cf8fd1ab.poster.avif?t=1770871236\" width=616 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/7a7c1b02226e48a114c43612cf8fd1ab.webm?t=1770871236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168100/extras/7a7c1b02226e48a114c43612cf8fd1ab.mp4?t=1770871236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></spa